{"tid":2339779,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"生左耶穌後，約瑟究竟有冇同瑪利亞做過愛","createTime":"2020-12-25T02:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T06:17:17.000Z","uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d47a3de45f6a7c795a34cd55805cf0baa83a2c40","tid":2339779,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:29:54.000Z","msg":"我先假設耶穌真係上帝令瑪利亞受孕<br />\n<br />\n聖經入面既約瑟，究竟係瑪利亞誕下耶穌後，二人有否做過愛<br />\n佢地之後究竟有冇夫妻之實？？<br />\n定係30年無性生活？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/atgwmKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatgwmKU.jpg&h=d0eae1da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完呢張圖我真係有個疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想睇下有冇基督徒或者宗教研究既人可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，究竟耶穌有冇兄弟姊妹？<br />\n<br />\n有啲版本好似講佢有兩個姊妹。<br />\n有啲版本好似話冇<br />\n<br />\n有兄弟姊妹，約瑟即係及後有同處子聖母做過愛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83281ebd56853df483c6ef5f35ccdafb8753899","tid":2339779,"uid":54728,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:30:12.000Z","msg":"Morning sir"},{"pid":"e9d97a4418fa782349433b145a6ae77c5264140b","tid":2339779,"uid":43785,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1c9qrc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1c9qrc1.jpg&h=b8479d0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37c281c45f9c3a485e1e723ffe27946ba01efc44","tid":2339779,"uid":102926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"morning Sir"},{"pid":"57b73cef052d54e7f5cfbf3eeb655eed770bf9d9","tid":2339779,"uid":184261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"你點做的"},{"pid":"2da63ab9924eb958445292682f5c564bd9cffa34","tid":2339779,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:30:27.000Z","msg":"S